description: The base object ID for this search instance; this is generated at the point of insertion into BigQuery.
name: id

description: The version of the extension; encoded as a four-digit number without dot points.
name: version

description: The activation code for the user.
name: hash_key

description: The user-agent string for the browser.
name: user_agent

description: The web browser program (e.g. Google Chrome)
name: browser_type

description: The keyword that was search (e.g. Apple)
name: keyword

description: The plugin ID that is provided by the browser's extension store.
name: plugin_id

description: The date at which the search instance was retrieved.
name: time_of_retrieval

description: The localised language setting of the browser (e.g. English).
name: localisation

description: The URL that was searched for this search instance.
name: url

description: Whether or not the user was logged into the search engine for this search instance.
name: logged_in

description: The approximated number of results returned for this search instance on the Google Videos search engine (desktop browsers only).
name: number_of_results_approximate

description: The approximate number of seconds taken to load the results given in the Google Videos search instance (desktop browsers only).
name: seconds_taken_to_load_approximate

description: The compressed list of titles for all suggestions presented on the page of this Google Videos search instance; reconstructs a list of JSON objects with the 'suggestion_image_thumbnail_list' field.
name: suggestion_title_list

description: The compressed list of images (either as a URL or Base64 string) for all suggestions presented on the page of this Google Videos search instance; reconstructs a list of JSON objects with the 'suggestion_title_list' field.
name: suggestion_image_thumbnail_list
